2022-01-19 00:45:57	mycroftiv	inhahe_: you use those experiences and psychology to tell a story, its the same idea
2022-01-19 00:45:57	<--	dude12312414 (~test@gateway/tor-sasl/dude12312414) has quit (Remote host closed the connection)
