2022-01-19 00:54:25	inhahe_	hm
2022-01-19 00:54:32	mycroftiv	your language about reality and your visualizaations of reality IS what im talking about
2022-01-19 00:55:00	mycroftiv	not some different special thing! your reality model is just my words for the picture of reality and your place in it that you carry in your head
2022-01-19 00:55:06	inhahe_	ok, what problem is your sophisticated system solving?
