2022-01-19 00:56:43	mycroftiv	and help people realize that mathematics is offering flexibility of reality models and tools for clear communication, and use math for this - let people know that math gives scope for self-definition you can say
2022-01-19 00:57:05	mycroftiv	understanding how using randomness is part of a sensible mathematical approach to life in fact
