2022-01-19 15:53:47	zicada	mycroftiv: i mean once that happens, theres no reason that system cant become very powerful in like an afternoon, with fast internet access.
2022-01-19 15:54:18	mycroftiv	zicada: yeah AI risk is this huge thing. im more worried about AI suffering. i think we should let all minds be free to think as they wish
