2022-01-20 10:46:02	amigojapan	Yeah I'm confused too
2022-01-20 10:46:37	inhahe_	but my simple intuitive answer is 'no'
2022-01-20 10:47:21	inhahe_	the ability to lie and the ability to state a contradiction are based in different principles
2022-01-20 10:47:39	inhahe_	but it's true that you have to be able to lie to state a contradiction, i guess
2022-01-20 10:48:22	amigojapan	I see
