2022-01-20 10:49:46	inhahe_	 i mean, without thinking about whatyou're saying
2022-01-20 10:50:08	inhahe_	i guess without knowing what you're saying
2022-01-20 10:50:22	amigojapan	Right, so it is not nessesarly a lie, so we can strike that
